---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 482
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=‘Duo Sunt in Homine’
  - 128
By: Hermes
---
Corporeal nature is your wife, O Soul, and intellect (vous) is your
father; and a blow given by your father’s hand is better than a kiss
given by your wife.
